{"schemaVersion":"gas-shunin-manual-law-explanation-audit/v1","reviewedAt":"2026-07-11","qualification":"gas-shunin-kou","examYear":2022,"sourceQuestionKey":"gas-shunin:kou:2022:law:q16","questionLabel":"問16","sourceQuestionBodyText":"法令で規定されている消費機器の技術上の基準に関する次の記述のうち、正しいものはいくつあるか。","sourceFile":"output/gas-shunin-kou/questions_json/2022/00_source/question_2022_firestore_2.json","explanationPatchFile":"output/gas-shunin-kou/questions_json/2022/21_explanationText_added/question_2022_firestore_2_explanationText_added.json","sourceCorrectChoiceText":["正しい","間違い","正しい","間違い","正しい"],"patchedCorrectChoiceText":["正しい","間違い","正しい","間違い","正しい"],"correctChoiceTextMatchesSource":true,"choiceReviews":[{"choiceIndex":0,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法施行規則第202条第1項第1号ロ"],"basisText":"所定の屋内ガス瞬間湯沸器には、原則として排気筒を設ける。"},{"choiceIndex":1,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["同項第2号イ(2)"],"basisText":"逆風止めは排気筒先端でなく、同一室内の燃焼器近接部に取り付ける。"},{"choiceIndex":2,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同項第3号イ・ハ"],"basisText":"排気扇の排気ガスに触れる材料は不燃性とし、停止時はガス供給を自動遮断する。"},{"choiceIndex":3,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["同項第6号リ"],"basisText":"天井裏等の排気部分は金属以外の不燃性材料で覆う。"},{"choiceIndex":4,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["同項第8号"],"basisText":"特定地下街等又は特定地下室等の燃焼器には所定のガス漏れ警報設備を設ける。"}],"changedFields":["explanationText","sourceExplanationCommonSummary","sourceExplanationChoiceSnippets","sourceExplanationChoiceCorrectness"],"result":"reviewed_and_rewritten","sourceUrls":["https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/345M50000400097"]}
